plot outline: In Vizag, a woman (Aamani) who hates the male domination in the society, approaches an ascetic woman and gets a herb named "Jamba Lakidi Pamba" which makes men behave like women and vice versa. Sent to find out the reason for this strange behaviour, a young cop (Naresh) travels to Vizag.
title: Jamba Lakidi Pamba
plot: A woman living in Visakhapatnam hates male domination in society and reverses the characteristics of men and women with the help of a magical herb.

In Vizag, a woman (Aamani) who hates the male domination in the society, approaches an ascetic woman and gets a herb named "_Jamba Lakidi Pamba_ (qv)" which makes men behave like women and vice versa. Sent to find out the reason for this strange behaviour, a young cop (Naresh) travels to Vizag.::Soumitra
